Original.

Illinois v. Michigan et al. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Morton, David R. Warner and Walter Kiechel, Jr. for the United States. Grenville Beardsley, Attorney General of Illinois, William C. Wines, Assistant Attorney General, George E. Billett, Charles A. Bane and Calvin D.
